{"id": 2351, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对“互联网的记忆只有七秒”最直观的体验是哪件事？", "description": "互联网有时候比我们想象得更健忘。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 19919, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180517193941cwdebaUy9skuoqRQ.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-20T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4180, "title": "你对“互联网的记忆只有七秒”最直观的体验是哪件事？", "content": "你对“互联网的记忆只有七秒”最直观的体验是哪件事？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 282328, "content": "去年火过的段子，今年换了一个号发，又上了一次热搜", "image": "img/option/option/20180518155205Zf5Vg0NCc8YSWHQx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282329, "content": "公共事件短时间内刷屏，很快大家连当事人叫啥都忘了", "image": "img/option/option/20180518155249t3FQ5lI1gAJakWTB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282330, "content": "短时间内发生同类公共事件，能被记住的只有一两个", "image": "img/option/option/20180518154915C4R5TU0ye8rSVuA1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282331, "content": "流量明星一段时间没新闻，再出现就让人感觉过气了", "image": "img/option/option/201805181536562FwDO8y7z6ARXVPY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282332, "content": "网络流行语过阵子就换一批", "image": "img/option/option/20180518131746uO8jkiCMogb5eRPq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282333, "content": "出现一百遍的经典谣言，改头换面再出现还有人上当", "image": "img/option/option/201805181309522KHXYoBTwUyjr7fx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282334, "content": "很多“流星式”app，凉的速度比火的速度还快", "image": "img/option/option/20180518120608XtPrvuWfBQRqYox0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282335, "content": "手机/电脑出了新款，老款出的问题就没啥人追究了", "image": "img/option/option/20180518114848meZsY5FfcL6agHy2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}